Function regexResult(searchVal, rxMainPattern, searchType As searchTypes)
'' Call this function to test `searchVal` against the regex pattern `rxMainPattern` along with the flag added based on `searchType`
    '' see examplesRegexResult for an example of this in use
    '' searchType is based on my own Enum `searchTypes` (at the top of the module)

''First two lines can be used as is.
